Text: RE Request MAPPF Reservation to be ANNULLEDIm sorry to inform you that your request to annul this reservation does not meet the criteria published in the Policies and Procedures posted on the OASIS Tom White MAPPCOR Original Message From mailto Sent Tuesday March PM To Subject Request MAPPF Reservation to be ANNULLED Enron requests Transcoord for MAPP Transmission Service to ANNUL reservation no The reason is as follows Reservation was requested at on for transmission service for mw during thru on NERC tag EPMI was submitted for the path AMRNNSPMAPPGRE and was subsequently denied by NSP and AMRN due to lack of ATC due to line outage EPMI rescheduled the energy on reservation s HE HE from NSP and DPC respectively Thank you in advance for your assistance on this matter Don Baughman Midwest Realtime Power Trading Supervisor Enron power Marketing Inc
